      <title>假期前交易清淡，货币在季末下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/em-currencies-miss-reform-led-emerging-market-rally-as-stocks-dollar-bonds-gain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，新兴市场货币连续第二天下跌，有望创下 2 月 14 日以来的最低收盘价，原因是美洲复活节假期前和本季度末交投清淡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/em-currencies-miss-reform-led-emerging-market-rally-as-stocks-dollar-bonds-gain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:48:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
